{"tid":1721222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"李氏主禱文，每晚你們都需要","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:20.000Z","uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e326e2e31529e96f66127b043f15d2e4c87efa2","tid":1721222,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:43.000Z","msg":": 我們在天上的超人,願人都尊李的名為姓。願李的國降臨,願李的旨意行在香港,如同行在長實。我們日用的物品,百佳賣給我們。免李家的稅,如同官府免窮人的福利。不叫我們遇到風球,救我們脫離黑雨。因為住屋,電力,交通,全是李的; 直到永遠。因李,及楷,及孫之名,阿門。"},{"pid":"9f7e7f2d4710a73312c704f240ff89d16b40e8a4","tid":1721222,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"906f531fbaa1a5830fc8481c265e722129e3ddec","tid":1721222,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}